name: Prism Seed
description:
Purchase this NFT, then send it from your wallet to prismcreate.tez (tz1XK6Dm72SpdiHPDbdoJN4nhVums16Qpyzm). You will then receive a 1/1 generative Prism, seeded from your wallet address. Please allow up to one day to arrive, as each has to be individually created. 

For more information about the Prism Collection and its rarity levels, visit chrisrandall.net
